Description: Provides comprehensive tools for biostatistics and clinical data 
    analysis including summary statistics, exploratory data analysis (EDA), 
    sample size calculation, statistical tests, data cleaning, transformation, 
    and visualization. Developed by the biostatistics team at Laboratorios 
    Sophia S.A. de C.V.
